    "As illustrated in Figure 10(f), the article employs deep learning algorithms and introduces a structured light network (SLN) for semantic recognition of the structured light images.",
    "The entire system achieves precise perception of object depth under lowlight conditions, demonstrating remarkable adaptability.",
    "AI-enhanced sensor systemsMetasurface can be designed to be particularly sensitive to small variations in specific physical parameters, making them suitable for creating highly sensitive sensors (metasensors) [213].",
    "Metasensor systems consist of metasensors, data acquisition, signal processing, and data output, and they are widely used in fields such as biology, chemistry, and optics to perceive and understand the properties and characteristics of substances and motion.",
    "AI plays a crucial role in metasensor systems, enabling rapid progress from sensor design to data processing."
